title: Average retail price for regular gasoline at self-service stations in Canada 2020
summary: The graph shows the Average retail price for regular gasoline in Canada 2020 .
The lowest Average is in Jannuary .
From February till July the graph oscillate .
gold: This graph describes the average retail price in Canada for regular gasoline during the year 2020 . In general , it shows that the average price was at its peak during January and rapidly declined over the next three months to below 80 cents/litre in April .
